  <brief_title>Evaluation of Post-traumatic Stress Among the Nearest Relatives of Brain-dead Organ Donors</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Post-traumatic Stress Among the Nearest Relatives of Brain-dead Organ Donors: Comparison With the Nearest-relatives of Brain-dead Patients Who Were Not Organ Donors for Medical or Legal Reasons, or Because of Donation Opposition</official_title>
  <sponsors>
