  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal is to compare post tramautic stress between the nearest relatives of brain-dead
      patients who are organ donor to those of brain-dead patients who are not organ donors for
      medical, legal or opposition reasons.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
